/*
 * HapticClient.cpp  -  Slave Side   (v5: Smith Predictor + Adaptive Jitter Buffer)
 * ==================================================================================
 * NEW in v5
 * ---------
 *  SMITH PREDICTOR (key S)
 *    - AR(2) model per axis with forgetting-factor RLS (lambda = 0.95)
 *    - Prediction horizon = RTT/2 (one-way delay, updated each tick)
 *    - EBA receives predicted remote position instead of stale received position
 *    - Eliminates perceptual delay: operator feels environment as if no network exists
 *    - Live display: predicted vs received position, AR coefficients, prediction error
 *
 *  ADAPTIVE JITTER BUFFER (key B)
 *    - RFC 3550 inter-packet jitter estimator (EWMA, 1/16 weight)
 *    - Adaptive playout delay target = sigma_jitter x k_factor + min_delay
 *    - k_factor increases under high jitter (conservative), shrinks under low (aggressive)
 *    - Sequence-ordered reorder buffer: holds packets up to reorder_timeout waiting
 *      for out-of-order arrivals before declaring a gap
 *    - Playout delay tracks up instantly on jitter spike, decays slowly on improvement
 *    - Smith Predictor fills the gap during increased buffer delay transparently
 *
 *  COMBINED OPERATION
 *    - Jitter buffer smooths the stream -> predictor compensates residual delay
 *    - Both independent toggles -> four operating modes for comparison:
 *        [off/off] raw delayed feedback
 *        [S/off]   prediction without buffering
 *        [off/B]   buffered but unpredicted
 *        [S/B]     full robust teleoperation  <- recommended
 *
 * All v4 features retained:
 *    Packet seq numbering, vertical candle labels, dual-line x-axis,
 *    artificial delay injection (D), candlestick charts, EBA+projection
 *
 * Keys
 * ----
 *  S       toggle Smith Predictor
 *  B       toggle Adaptive Jitter Buffer
 *  D       toggle artificial delay (for testing)
 *  ,  .    constant delay +/-5 ms   |  N M  jitter +/-5 ms
 *  E / P   EBA / Projection       |  1    force field
 *  +/-     candle window  [ ]  preset   ESC quit
 *
 * *** SET SERVER_IP ***
 */

